Morphology of 
<taxonomicName authority="Yin, 2022" authorityName="Yin" authorityYear="2022" box="[460,748,1352,1376]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Arthromelodes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="58" pageNumber="59" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="songxiaobini" status="sp. nov.">
