</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[756,838,1353,1377]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[756,838,1353,1377]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
(A–G. Male. H. Female). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1113,1138,1352,1376]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59">A.</emphasis>
Dorsal habitus. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1308,1331,1353,1377]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59">B.</emphasis>
Head and pronotum. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[263,287,1388,1412]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59">C.</emphasis>
Mesotibia. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[409,434,1389,1413]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59">D.</emphasis>
Tergites 4 and 5 (VII and VIII). 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[770,793,1389,1413]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59">E.</emphasis>
